OL,3,CWhat can we expect in next week's
OL,4,Cbudget and what does it mean for Wales?
OL,6,FThe Chancellor Of the Exchequer will
OL,7,Funveil her budget on November 26,
OL,8,Fsetting out details of the UK
OL,9,FGovernment's spending for the next
OL,10,Ffinancial year.
OL,12,FIt's already politically
OL,13,Fcontroversial, with warnings of tax
OL,14,Frises and reports of u-turns, while
OL,15,Fhere in Wales it could help or hinder
OL,16,FLabour's chances of heading off an
OL,17,Felection nightmare next year.
