OL,3,CWhat can we expect in next week's
OL,4,Cbudget and what does it mean for Wales?
OL,6,FDecisions that Rachel Reeves announces
OL,7,Fon Wednesday could affect each one of
OL,8,Fus with predicted changes to taxes,
OL,9,Fbenefits and pension rules.
OL,11,FEluned Morgan's Welsh Government will
OL,12,Fwant to know if it has any extra
OL,13,Ffunding as a result of spending in
OL,14,FEngland. That would give her certainty
OL,15,Fon the final amount she has to spend
OL,16,Fin its own budget on which she is
OL,17,Fstill trying to reach a deal with the
OL,18,Fother parties.
