OL,6,FThis has proven to be a source of
OL,7,Fcontroversy and confusion for the UK
OL,8,FGovernment. In the 2024 UK General
OL,9,FElection, Labour pledged not to raise
OL,10,Fnational insurance contributions
OL,11,F(NICs), income tax or VAT.
OL,13,FRachel Reeves increased employer NICs
OL,14,Fin her 2024 budget and it was expected
OL,15,Fthat, in this year's budget, she would
OL,16,Fincrease income tax by 2p and reduce
OL,17,Femployees' NICs by the same amount.
