OL,4,Cbudget and what does it mean for Wales?
OL,6,FThe Chancellor is having to raise tax
OL,7,Fbecause u-turns on previous revenue-
OL,8,Fraising moves such as cutting winter
OL,9,Ffuel payments, and a worsening
OL,10,Feconomic picture have left her with a
OL,11,Fblack hole in the public finances,
OL,12,Fthought to be between #20bn and #30bn.
OL,14,FChild Poverty
OL,16,FIt's thought that the Chancellor could
OL,17,Fuse the budget to say whether or not
OL,18,Fthe controversial two-child benefit
OL,19,Fcap will be lifted either partially or
OL,20,Fin full.
