OL,4,Cbudget and what does it mean for Wales?
OL,6,FSome reports suggest that tax could be
OL,7,Fset at 3p per mile charge, costing the
OL,8,Faverage EV driver around #250 a year.
OL,10,FBut the MD of Ford UK, Lisa Brankin,
