OL,3,CWhat can we expect in next week's
OL,4,Cbudget and what does it mean for Wales?
OL,6,FIt's been reported that Rachel Reeves
OL,7,Fis looking at capping what's known as
OL,8,F'salary sacrifice' for pension
OL,9,Fcontributions at #2,000 a year.
OL,11,FSalary sacrifice is a way that allows
OL,12,Femployees to pay less income tax and
OL,13,FNICs on a reduced salary in return for
OL,14,Fa non-cash benefit such as pension
OL,15,Fcontributions, childcare, or extra
OL,16,Fholidays.
